Package com.intellij.psi

Interface JavaCodeFragment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iconable, Navigatable, NavigatablePsiElement, NavigationItem, PsiCheckedRenameElement, PsiCodeFragment, PsiElement, PsiFile, PsiFileSystemItem, PsiImportHolder, PsiNamedElement, UserDataHolder
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PsiExpressionCodeFragment, PsiJavaCodeReferenceCodeFragment, PsiTypeCodeFragment
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GroovyCodeFragment, GroovyShellCodeFragment, PsiCodeFragmentImpl, PsiExpressionCodeFragmentImpl, PsiJavaCodeReferenceCodeFragmentImpl, PsiTypeCodeFragmentImpl

    public interface JavaCodeFragment
extends PsiImportHolder, PsiCodeFragment
    Represents a fragment of Java code which exists outside of a project structure (for example, in a foreign language code or in a user interface element other than the main source code editor).
